---
title: "US58 — Manage expert categories"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>CategoriesScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ManageExpertCategories
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertCategory
  alt create
    A->>B: enter name, tap ADD CATEGORY
    B->>C: create(name)
    C->>E: insertExpertCategory(name)
    E-->>C: ExpertCategory (new)
  else rename
    A->>B: edit name, tap SAVE
    B->>C: rename(categoryId, name)
    C->>E: updateExpertCategory(categoryId, name)
    E-->>C: ExpertCategory (updated)
  else remove
    A->>B: tap DELETE
    B->>C: remove(categoryId)
    C->>E: deleteExpertCategory(categoryId)
    E-->>C: ok
  end
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (categories)
  B-->>A: marketplace filters reflect the change
  note over E: insertExpertCategory / updateExpertCategory / deleteExpertCategory via SupabaseGateway (RLS admin-only)
